	<text xml:lang="la">
		<body>
			<div>
				<p>
					<s n="1" xml:lang="la" type="auto">S. D.</s>
					<s n="2" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Accepi tuas expectatissimas, charissime <persName ref="p8418" cert="high">Myconi</persName>, per <persName type="citizen_name" ref="p7070" cert="high">H(einrychum) Wirtium</persName>, quem commendasti.</s>
					<s n="3" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Ego illum libenter iuvabo, quantum possum salva conscientia, idque propter tuam commendationem.</s>
					<s n="4" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Postulavi ab ipso literas, quas vocant testimonii, scriptas a ministris ecclesiae <placeName type="auto_name">Doggianae</placeName>; eas expecto.</s>
					<s n="5" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Vixit alioqui hucusque satis libidinose et exercuit usuram; mercator enim fuit etc.</s>
				</p>
				<p>
					<s n="6" xml:lang="de" type="auto"><foreign xml:lang="la">De <placeName ref="l457" cert="high">Constantiensibus</placeName> hoc habeo:</foreign> "Unser botten ligend zuͦ <placeName type="citizen_name" ref="l18" cert="high">Augspurg</placeName> und wie man fürgäben, so wir uns ergäbind und gnad begärind, werde nit me von uns erfordert, ist es jetzung ein anders, und wil man mitt den botten vorhin articulieren.</s>
				</p>
				<p>
					<s n="7" xml:lang="de" type="auto">Also gadt es" etc.</s>
				</p>
				<p>
					<s n="8" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Capita Interim accepi ab <placeName ref="l1976" cert="high">Augusta</placeName>, de quo tu meliora accepisti, quam revera res ipsa habeat.</s>
					<s n="9" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Certe quo ab initio disputantur de statu hominis ante et post lapsum, de servitute et captivitate, de libertate et redemptione hominis per Christum, de iustificatione etc. non omnino impia dicuntur esse.</s>
					<s n="10" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Sed reliqua de 7 sacramentis, de incarnatione et intercessione sanctorum, de festis, ceremoniis, missis, oratione per mortuis etc. plane papistica sunt et quae doctrinam sanam de Christo subvertunt.</s>
					<s n="11" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Lusit ergo quidam in Interim: <persName type="auto_name">Caesar Carolus</persName> Interim pudendum, <persName type="auto_name">Mendax</persName>, falsiloquu dolisque plenum Finxit.</s>
					<s n="12" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Si: Quid id est requiris, audi: Forma est, qua pietas fidesque vera Et quicquid superest in orbe sancti Ceu diro misere interit veneno.</s>
				</p>
				<p>
					<s n="13" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Certe oportebit nos probari.</s>
					<s n="14" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Qui perseveraverit in finem usque, salvus erit.</s>
					<s n="15" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Articulus de eucharistia transubstantionem et adorationem retinet mordicus etc.</s>
				</p>
				<p>
					<s n="16" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Scis <persName ref="p8018" cert="high">Hallerum</persName> a nostris postulatum <placeName ref="l41" cert="high">Bernam</placeName> esse missum.</s>
					<s n="17" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Audio <persName type="citizen_name" ref="p8364" cert="high">Battum</persName><note xml:id="fn1" type="footnote" n="1"><persName ref="p8364" cert="high">Beat Gering</persName>.</note> et <persName type="citizen_name" ref="p3099" cert="high">Sulcerum</persName> <placeName type="citizen_name" ref="l28" cert="high">Basileam</placeName> concessuros.</s>
					<s n="18" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Tuum fuerit diligenter curare, ut ecclesia vestra in tranquillitate maneat.</s>
				</p>
				<p>
					<s n="19" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Vale et me, ut soles, ama.</s>
					<s n="20" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Nova habeo plura, sed quae dubia apud me sunt; nolui his te gravare.</s>
					<s n="21" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Vale.</s>
				</p>
				<p>
					<s n="22" xml:lang="la" type="auto"><placeName ref="l587" type="citizen_name" cert="high">Tiguri</placeName> 14. maii 1548.</s>
				</p>
				<p>
					<s n="23" xml:lang="la" type="auto"><persName ref="p495" type="citizen_name" cert="high">Bullingerus</persName> tuus.</s>
				</p>
				<p>
					<note type="address">[Adresse:]</note>
					<s n="24" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Praestantissimo viro D. <persName type="citizen_name" ref="p8418" cert="high">Osvaldo Myconio</persName>, domino et fratri semper colendo suo.</s>
					<s n="25" xml:lang="de" type="auto"><placeName ref="l28" cert="high">Basel</placeName>.</s>
				</p>
			</div>
		</body>
	</text>
